286
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:19,713
Rentre chez toi.

287
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:21,873
Tu ne peux pas me sauver.

288
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,478
Tu en es sûr?

289
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:32,038
